Achievements.Name: Kung-Fu Hero
Achievements.Description: Complete the story mode.

Achievements.Name: Earthquake!
Achievements.Description: Damage 7 or more enemies with one Ground Shaker.

Achievements.Name: Lightning Rod
Achievements.Description: Defeat 8 or more enemies using Lightning in a single fight (Inklings don't count).

Achievements.Name: Power Punisher
Achievements.Description: Hit an enemy from behind with Power Punch. Do this 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Bullseye!
Achievements.Description: Use Magic Bow to hit an enemy at least 15m away. Do this 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Pick on Someone Your Own Size
Achievements.Description: Finish off a Giant while giant-sized yourself.

Achievements.Name: Wham!
Achievements.Description: Finish off an Armored Inkling while Damage Boost is active.

Achievements.Name: Fast as Lightning
Achievements.Description: Defeat 10 enemies within 10 seconds (Inklings don't count).

Achievements.Name: Inkling Combo Master
Achievements.Description: Hit inklings so they collide with other enemies. Do this 200 times.

Achievements.Name: Inkling Bullseye
Achievements.Description: Hit an inkling so it collides with another enemy at least 6m away. Do this 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Last Man Standing
Achievements.Description: Reach round 10 in Survival.

Achievements.Name: The Professional
Achievements.Description: Defeat 200 enemies in Time Trial (5 minutes).

Achievements.Name: Master of Not Getting Hit
Achievements.Description: Reach a time of 3:30 in Don't Get Hit.

Achievements.Name: Inkling Hunter
Achievements.Description: Complete the Inkling Hunt with a time lower than 1:15.

Achievements.Name: Black Belt
Achievements.Description: Reach total skill level 10.

Achievements.Name: Kung-Fu Master
Achievements.Description: Reach total skill level 21.

Achievements.Name: Kung-Fu Club Champion
Achievements.Description: Win all rounds of Kung-Fu Club.

Achievements.Name: King of the Hill
Achievements.Description: Survive at least 2 minutes in King of the Hill.

Achievements.Name: The Big Boss
Achievements.Description: Defeat Sym in Chapter 14 without using Lightning, Time Stop or Damage Boost.

Achievements.Name: Slow Motion Master
Achievements.Description: Hit 5 different enemies during a single Time Stop.
